item.title: 【Requests】[REQ VID] - Christmas with Delta ( 2023 ).
item.description:
Hi, By any chance did anyone on here record the Delta Goodrem TV Special last night in 1080p ?

Christmas with Delta

A Christmas concert with Delta Goodrem. Featuring Robbie Williams, G Flip, Budjerah, Kate Ceberano, Jon Stevens, Bebe Rexha, David Campbell, Rai Thistlethwaite, Teddy Swims and a special performance by Russell Crowe.

It is being repeated - But, the show last night went for 2 hours - the repeat ( So, the TV Guide shows is only an Hour ?? )

Hopefully, someone did record it and can upload it here. Thanks
